cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV 

The paper discusses a method for learning data-driven models to improve control and planning algorithms. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO), as well as systems and control (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV) which are all relevant to the development of autonomous systems.
